==English==

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /ræŋk/
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æŋk|-æŋk]]

===Etymology===
Old English ''[[ranc]]''
====Adjective====
{{en-adj-more}}

# Having a very strong and bad [[odor]].
# Highly offensive; disgusting.

